    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed; achieved levels meet required levels at MRL 5. Monte Carlo UQ confirms 95th-percentile NIH below clinical threshold. One open item noted: the primary experimental hemolysis dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-31) predates the February 2026 model revision (modelRevisionDate 2026-02-14); re-validation against the revised geometry is planned for Q2 2026. Assessment team accepted the package on the basis that geometric changes are minor (impeller tip clearance ±0.05 mm) and sensitivity analysis shows NIH change < 2%. Re-validation results must be submitted before next design review.",
